+--      DTN 12/14/95  UPDATED ACVC VERSION STRING TO
+--                    "ACVC 2.1".
+--      EDS 12/17/97  UPDATED ACVC VERSION STRING TO
+--                    "2.2".
+--      RLB  3/16/00  UPDATED ACATS VERSION STRING TO "2.3".
+--                    CHANGED VARIOUS STRINGS TO READ "ACATS".
